      "comment_id" : 38883475,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "<a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/a/25007019/589259\">Added an answer</a> that uses <code>Collections.unmodifiableList(list)</code> as assignment to the field, to make sure that the list isn&#39;t changed by the class itself."
    }, {
      "owner" : {
